<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_02_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema521_su_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_02_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">지유네 모둠의 제자리멀리뛰기 기록을 나타낸 표입니다. 145와 같거나 작은 수를 나타내는 방법을 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">기록이 145 ㎝와 같거나 짧은 학생의 기록을 모두 선택해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="long_jump">
            <h4 class="tit" lang="y">학생별 제자리멀리뛰기 기록</h4>

            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">이름</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">기록(㎝)</span>
              </div>

              <button class="item" data-answer-single="true">
                <span class="name" lang="y">지유</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">143</span>
              </button>

              <button class="item" data-answer-single="false">
                <span class="name" lang="y">승민</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">147.8</span>
              </button>

              <button class="item" data-answer-single="true">
                <span class="name" lang="y">채희</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">145</span>
              </button>

              <button class="item" data-answer-single="true">
                <span class="name" lang="y">우진</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">144.6</span>
              </button>

              <button class="item" data-answer-single="false">
                <span class="name" lang="y">민서</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">148</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">145와 같거나 작은 수를 어떻게 나타내면 좋을지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="long_jump">
            <h4 class="tit" lang="y">학생별 제자리멀리뛰기 기록</h4>

            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">이름</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">기록(㎝)</span>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">지유</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">143</span>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">승민</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">147.8</span>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">채희</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">145</span>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">우진</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">144.6</span>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <span class="name" lang="y">민서</span>
                <span class="record" lang="y">148</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">‘같거나’, ‘작은 수’의 앞 글자를 따서 145와 같작 수라고 부르면 좋을 것 같습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize">
              <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>

              <div>
                <span lang="y">143, 144.6, 145와 같이 145와 같거나 작은 수를 145</span>
                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="1" lang="y">이하</button>
                <span lang="y">인 수라고 합니다.</span>
              </div>

              <div>
                <span lang="y">145 이하인 수를 그림에 나타내면 다음과 같습니다.</span>
              </div>

              <div class="cont_set">
                <div class="left-side">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA521_02_SU/0004_check_content.png" alt="자 이미지" />

                  <p class="t01" lang="y">142</p>
                  <p class="t02" lang="y">143</p>
                  <p class="t03" lang="y">144</p>
                  <p class="t04" lang="y">145</p>
                  <p class="t05" lang="y">146</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
